    "GAT's attention mechanisms allow it to focus on relevant parts of a graph and increase model performance.",
    "For instance, in the case of DeepDDS (Wang et al. 2022a), GAT is used to gather important information from the structure of drugs.",
    "Additionally, Zhang et al.",
    "(Zhang et al. 2023) and Hu et al.",
    "(Hu et al. 2023) take a knowledge graph (KG) approach, creating graphs and using Graph Attention Networks to gather valuable insights from these graphs."
